snippet.title: PS4, NSW | Kamen Rider Memory of Heroez 2nd Trailer Released
snippet.description: Prepare to face against the battle for humanity! Team up with Double, OOO and Zero-One to test the power of the Core Strength, and uncover the mystery of the "accident". All in the name of justice! Kamen Rider Memory of Heroez arrives on 29th October 2020 for PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch. #KamenRider #BandaiNamco
